data.description: Welcome to this beautiful turn-key home with NO HOA, offering a perfect blend of comfort and style. Upon entering, the family room welcomes you with gleaming hardwood floors, creating an inviting atmosphere that flows seamlessly into the elegant dining room. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring updated quartz countertops, a stylish backsplash, and modern appliances.  The main level boasts two generously sized bedrooms, complemented by a convenient Jack and Jill bathroom, making it an ideal setup for main-level living. Step outside onto the covered porch, leading to a deck where you can savor your morning coffee or immerse yourself in the beauty of nature.  Descend to the spacious rec room, perfect for entertaining or simply cozying up in front of the fireplace. This lower level also offers two potential non-legal bedrooms and a full bath, providing flexibility and ample space. The walk-out basement extends the entertainment options to a concrete patio and gazebo, creating a delightful outdoor retreat.  Noteworthy features include a recently replaced roof (2 years old), a newer hot water heater, and a septic system that was updated 8 years ago, ensuring the home is well-maintained. Revel in the privacy of this retreat, away from the hustle and bustle, while still being minutes away from grocery stores and dining options. The house also come with a generator for added convenience. This home offers the perfect combination of modern amenities, thoughtful updates, and a serene setting.     Open House Saturday, December 2nd 2023 from 12pm - 2pm  Accepting Back up Offers
